<plot>Burn is the story of two men and the destiny they both share. Robert Elektra spends his days in a drug induced haze, consumed by hatred at the society that ignores him and filled with guilt after the murder of his parents some years before. Robert's world is suddenly turned inside out when a mysterious stranger offers him a large sum of money to find his missing daughter, Anna and bring her home.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087116</url></doc>
